The K8s code can be found here: https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/pkg/kubelet/kuberuntime/logs/logs.go#L128

Considering CRI-O is using more and more libpod code, I propose to add the logging functionality to `libpod` such that Podman and CRI-O (and any other libpod user) can take advantage of that.

@baude @mheon @umohnani8 @rhatdan WDYT?
